lyrics:
[Verse]
In the land of riffs and rhythm, there's a legend we all know
Misha, the god of kanabis with a power that won't slow
He strums his guitar with fire, unleashing explosive sound
A master of the music, his presence is renowned

[Chorus]
Misha, the god of kanabis, his melodies ignite
With every note he plays, we transcend to greater heights
His strings weave tales of passion, his music sets us free
Misha, the god of kanabis, we bow down on bended knee
